<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Bienvenido a Vayven API</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            transition: all 300ms ease;
        }
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: #fff;
        }
        .container {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem;
            max-width: 800px;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            animation: fadeInDown 0.8s ease;
        }
        .subtitle {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            opacity: 0.9;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease 0.2s both;
        }
        .description {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            opacity: 0.8;
            animation: fadeIn 0.8s ease 0.4s both;
        }
        .endpoints {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 2rem;
            margin-top: 2rem;
            text-align: left;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease 0.6s both;
        }
        .endpoints h2 {
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
        }
        .endpoint-item {
            padding: 0.75rem;
            margin: 0.5rem 0;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
        .method {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem;
            border-radius: 3px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-right: 0.5rem;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
        }
        .get { background: #61affe; }
        .post { background: #49cc90; }
        .put { background: #fca130; }
        .delete { background: #f93e3e; }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 3rem;
            opacity: 0.7;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            animation: fadeIn 1s ease 0.8s both;
        }
        @keyframes fadeInDown {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(-20px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }
        @keyframes fadeInUp {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(20px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }
        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; }
            to { opacity: 1; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>üöÄ Vayven API</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">API RESTful con Node.js + Express</p>
        <p class="description">
            Sistema de gesti√≥n de unidades de transporte construido con Node.js, Express y MySQL.
            Migrado exitosamente desde CodeIgniter 4 (PHP) a Node.js.
        </p>

        <div class="endpoints">
            <h2>üì° Endpoints Disponibles</h2>
            
            <div class="endpoint-item">
                <span class="method get">GET</span>
                <code>/api/unidad</code> - Listar todas las unidades
            </div>
            
            <div class="endpoint-item">
                <span class="method post">POST</span>
                <code>/api/unidad/agregar</code> - Crear nueva unidad
            </div>
            
            <div class="endpoint-item">
                <span class="method put">PUT</span>
                <code>/api/unidad/editar/:id</code> - Actualizar unidad
            </div>
            
            <div class="endpoint-item">
                <span class="method delete">DELETE</span>
                <code>/api/unidad/eliminar/:id</code> - Eliminar unidad
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>Desarrollado con ‚ù§Ô∏è usando Node.js <%= new Date().getFullYear() %></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
